# ── Harness configuration ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets are SHARED across all worktrees in:
#
#     ~/.config/neokapi/harness.env   (honours $XDG_CONFIG_HOME)
#
# Put GEMINI_API_KEY there once and every checkout/worktree reuses it. This
# per-worktree harness/.env is OPTIONAL and only for one-off local overrides
# (it is loaded first and wins over the shared file). Copy to `.env` to use.

# Required for the AI / narration demos (normally lives in the shared file):
# GEMINI_API_KEY=

# Narration backend selection (operational toggle, default: gemini):
#   gemini | elevenlabs | openai | say
# NARRATION_BACKEND=gemini
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=
# ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# NOTE: narration pace/tone tuning is NOT configurable here — it lives in
# committed code constants (src/narrate/synth.ts) so delivery is identical on
# every machine and in CI.
#
# NOTE: the repo path is auto-detected from the enclosing checkout. Set the
# NEOKAPI_REPO *environment variable* only for a standalone harness checkout.
